;a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Rahul Bansal\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2088:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-142358\" src=\"https://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/pn4-720x276.png\" alt=\"pn4\" width=\"640\" height=\"245\" srcset=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/pn4-400x153.png 400w, https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/pn4-768x294.png 768w, https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/pn4-720x276.png 720w, https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/pn4.png 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" />PressNomics is, as it describes itself &#8220;The conference for those that power the WordPress Economy&#8221;.</p>\n<p>As rtCamp is part of WordPress economy, we decided to attend the conference this year and felt that it was also important to be a sponsor in some way.</p>\n<p>We are proud to be community sponsors for <a href=\"http://pressnomics.com/\">PressNomics</a>.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Please welcome <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rtCamp\">@rtcamp</a> as a Community-Level sponsor. (wicked great nginx configs for WP) <a href=\"https://t.co/TUzx7JFwII\">pic.twitter.com/TUzx7JFwII</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; PressNomics (@PressNomics) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PressNomics/status/693130892340912128\">January 29, 2016</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>Since I am attending PressNomics4, I would love to meet up with fellow community members. If you want to have a word, discuss building a WordPress based agency in India, I would love being part of such discussions.</p>\n<p>You can simply tweet me <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rahul286\">@rahul286</a> to catchup or leave a comment on this blog post. The best way to recognise me would be look out for a guy wearing a t-shirt with rtCamp logo.</p>\n<p><strong>Link:</strong> <a href=\"http://pressnomics.com/\">PressNomics</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/pressnomics-4-catch-up/\">Let’s Catch Up at PressNomics4</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/pressnomics-4-catch-up/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"Wufoo to Gravity Forms importer WordPress plugin is now Free!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/migrate-wufoo-form-gravity-form-free/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/migrate-wufoo-form-gravity-form-free/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 02 Feb 2016 14:12:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://rtcamp.com/?p=140646\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:401:\"<p>We are making our Wufoo to Gravity Forms WordPress plugin free. We are releasing the code on Github and it is also available on WordPress plugin repo.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/migrate-wufoo-form-gravity-form-free/\">Wufoo to Gravity Forms importer WordPress plugin is now Free!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Nitun Lanjewar\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1734:\"<p>Few years ago we released <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/wufoo-to-gravity-forms-importer/\">Wufoo to Gravity content importer plugin</a>. We got a good response from users in terms of enhancements to add and also feedback.</p>\n<p>We are organising our list of premium plugins and felt that there were many who wanted to migrate their Wufoo form data to Gravity Forms. It would be better to actually offer this plugin as a free plugin back to the community.</p>\n<p>You can now download use this plugin from the official <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/migrate-wufoo-to-gravity-forms/\">WordPress plugin directory</a>.</p>\n<p>The plugin&#8217;s code can be found on <a href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/migrate-wufoo-to-gravity-forms\">Github</a>. If you want to report any issues or need to make changes, feel free to send us a pull request.</p>\n<p>If you have already purchased this plugin from our store, you can use our <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/premium-support/\">premium support</a>  if you need any assistance.</p>\n<p>Your plugin license key is valid for one year as mentioned <a href=\"http://docs.rtcamp.com/license/\">license key</a> will not restrict any feature of the plugin, it was just used to give future updates and premium support.</p>\n<p><strong>Links</strong>: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/migrate-wufoo-to-gravity-forms/\">Wufoo to Gravity content importer plugin</a> | <a href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/migrate-wufoo-to-gravity-forms\">Github</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/migrate-wufoo-form-gravity-form-free/\">Wufoo to Gravity Forms importer WordPress plugin is now Free!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/migrate-wufoo-form-gravity-form-free/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"Shmart Payment Gateway Addon for Easy Digital Downloads is Free\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-addon-easy-digital-downloads-free/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 21 Jan 2016 14:47:17 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://rtcamp.com/?p=140643\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:443:\"<p>The Shmart Payment Gateway Addon for Easy Digital Downloads allows using Shmart payment gateway with your EasyDigitalDownload store and is now part of the official WordPress plugin repo.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-addon-easy-digital-downloads-free/\">Shmart Payment Gateway Addon for Easy Digital Downloads is Free</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aditya Kane\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1647:\"<p>Few months ago we introduced <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-payment-gateway-easy-digital-downloads-plugin/\">Shmart Payment Gateway addon</a> for Easy Digital Downloads plugin. This plugin add-on was mainly developed by us for our <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/products/\">store</a> that runs on Easy Digital Downloads. We are streamlining our product line and decided to make some of our premium plugins available free.</p>\n<h2>What is Shmart?</h2>\n<p>It is a payment gateway that is very popular in India.  <a href=\"http://shmart.in/\">Shmart Payment Gateway</a> allows users to purchase the product in Indian currency (INR). It also accepts payments via all VISA and MasterCard debit and credit cards and internet banking of 27 major banks and IMPS payment option with over 55 banks.</p>\n<p>This add-on that allows using Shmart payment gateway with your EasyDigitalDownload store is now part of the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/payment-gateway-easy-digital-downloads-shmart/\">official WordPress plugin repo</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Links: </strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/payment-gateway-easy-digital-downloads-shmart/\">Shmart Payment Gateway for EDD Addon</a> | <a href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/payment-gateway-easydigitaldownloads-shmart\">Github</a> | <a href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/payment-gateway-easydigitaldownloads-shmart/wiki\">Documentation</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-addon-easy-digital-downloads-free/\">Shmart Payment Gateway Addon for Easy Digital Downloads is Free</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"WordPress 4.4 is 10th consecutive release with contribution from rtCampers\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/wordpress-4-4-10th-consecutive-release-contribution-rtcampers/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 09 Dec 2015 14:27:01 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"Wordpress Core Contribution\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://rtcamp.com/?p=136759\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:497:\"<p>WordPress 4.4 a little extra special for rtCamp is that it\'s the 10th consecutive WordPress release with a contribution from an rtCamper. This time we have 7 rtCampers who made it to the list as contributors!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/wordpress-4-4-10th-consecutive-release-contribution-rtcampers/\">WordPress 4.4 is 10th consecutive release with contribution from rtCampers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aditya Kane\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2144:\"<p>In the wee hours of the morning here in India, WordPress 4.4 &#8220;Clifford&#8221; was released. It is named &#8220;Clifford&#8221; in honor of jazz trumpeter Clifford Brown.</p>\n<p>The big change for most users with WordPress 4.4 is the new Twenty-Sixteen default theme.</p>\n<p>Along with that change the really big announcement is the integration of REST API infrastructure into WordPress core. This will enable developers to build and extend RESTful APIs on top of WordPress.</p>\n<p>You can read more about <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2015/12/clifford/\">WordPress 4.4 &#8220;Clifford&#8221; at its release post</a>.<br />\n<script src=\"https://videopress.com/videopress-iframe.js\"></script></p>\n<h2>rtCampers contributing to core</h2>\n<p>What marks out WordPress 4.4 a little extra special for rtCamp is that it&#8217;s the 10th consecutive WordPress release with a contribution from an rtCamper. This time we have 7 rtCampers who made it to the list as contributors!</p>\n<p>Congratulations to Prasad Nevase, Umesh Nevase, Dipesh Kakadiya, Utkarsh Patel, Juhi Saxena, Mehul Kaklotkar and Sanket Parmar.</p>\n<p>Also congratulations to 8 ex-rtCampers Ankit Gade, Ankit K Gupta, Gagan Deep Singh, Umesh Kumar, Chirag Swadia, Paresh Radadiya, Hrishikesh Vaipurkar, Sumit Singh who also are on the list.</p>\n<h2>Compatibility with WordPress 4.4</h2>\n<p>We have been testing our plugins and themes with WordPress 4.4 and they all work great with the new version. In case you have any questions or concerns feel free to raise a <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/premium-support/\">support ticket for your product</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Link:</strong> <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2015/12/clifford/\">WordPress 4.4 Release Post</a> | <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/tag/wordpress-core-contribution/\">rtCamp’s WordPress Core Contributions Archive</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/wordpress-4-4-10th-consecutive-release-contribution-rtcampers/\">WordPress 4.4 is 10th consecutive release with contribution from rtCampers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"Our EasyEngine project now has a dedicated website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/easyengine-dedicated-website/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/easyengine-dedicated-website/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 27 Nov 2015 06:20:03 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"EasyEngine\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Nginx\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://rtcamp.com/?p=131859\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:334:\"<p>Introducing EasyEngine.io, our new dedicated website for our server management tool called EasyEngine.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/easyengine-dedicated-website/\">Our EasyEngine project now has a dedicated website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aditya Kane\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2361:\"<p>At rtCamp we have many products that are WordPress plugins and themes. Along with that we also have EasyEngine which is a server management tool that makes using WordPress on Nginx easy. Having such a wide variety of products so different in size, scope and technology at a single place was getting difficult.</p>\n<p>Hence over the past couple of months, the EasyEngine team started working on a new dedicated website, <a href=\"https://easyengine.io\">EasyEngine.io</a> for the project.</p>\n<h2>What has changed!</h2>\n<p>The project now has a dedicated website but we have also moved some other sections to EasyEngine.io from this website. Here is a list of them.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>https://rtcamp.com/easyengine/ redirects to new site <a href=\"https://easyengine.io/\">https://easyengine.io/</a></li>\n<li>http://docs.rtcamp.com/easyengine/ redirects to <a href=\"https://easyengine.io/docs\">https://easyengine.io/docs</a></li>\n<li>The WordPress-Nginx section also has been moved to <a href=\"https://easyengine.io/services/\">https://easyengine.io/services/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/easyengine/\">New Github Org</a>. https://github.com/rtCamp/easyengine redirects to <a href=\"https://github.com/easyengine/easyengine\">https://github.com/easyengine/easyengine</a></li>\n<li>New mailing list. <em>Old subscribers from rtcamp.com have already been moved.</em></li>\n<li>Social media profiles – <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/easyengine\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/117491501258021876478\">Google Plus</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/easyengine\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/easyengine\">LinkedIn</a>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Read more about the new website at <a href=\"https://easyengine.io/blog/new-website-slack-team/\">this dedicated blog for EasyEngine</a>.</p>\n<p>The new website will allow us to manage the project and also serve the users in the future in a more focused and an integrated way.</p>\n<p><strong>Link: </strong><a href=\"https://easyengine.io\">EasyEngine.io</a> | <a href=\"https://easyengine.io/blog/new-website-slack-team/\">EasyEngine.io announcement</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/easyengine-dedicated-website/\">Our EasyEngine project now has a dedicated website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/easyengine-dedicated-website/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"Thanks for being with us – here’s something for you!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/thanksgiving-promo-2015/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 25 Nov 2015 12:24:30 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Promo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Discount\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"rtMedia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\