hanksgiving Promo Code\" width=\"600\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/thanks20-rtcamp-400x187.jpg 400w, https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/thanks20-rtcamp.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Use the coupon code <strong>THANKS20</strong> to avail the discount. The offer will start from <strong>26th November</strong> and will end on <strong>30th November</strong>.</p>\n<p>We would also like to hear more from you on your experience using rtMedia. If you are happy with rtMedia, please<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/buddypress-media?filter=5#postform\"> share your feedback on wordpress.org</a>.</p>\n<p>If you are a facing any issue, please use our <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/premium-support/\">premium support</a> or post in <a href=\"http://community.rtcamp.com/c/rtmedia\">community forum</a> to get help. We are always working hard to improve rtMedia and any feedback will help us immensely.</p>\n<p>Thanks again! <img src=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png\" alt=\":-)\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p><a class=\"primary button\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/products/category/rtmedia/\">BUY NOW</a> <a class=\"button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/buddypress-media?filter=5#postform\">SHARE YOUR FEEDBACK</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/thanksgiving-promo-2015/\">Thanks for being with us – here&#8217;s something for you!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Let’s Catch Up at WordCamp US 2015\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/lets-catch-up-wordcamp-us-2015/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 23 Nov 2015 15:21:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WordCamp US\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://rtcamp.com/?p=131006\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:241:\"<p>Let’s catch up!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/lets-catch-up-wordcamp-us-2015/\">Let&#8217;s Catch Up at WordCamp US 2015</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Rahul Bansal\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1945:\"<p>Last year, I visited <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/easyengines-usa-trip/\">San Francisco as a speaker at NginxConf</a>. Since <a href=\"https://sf.wordcamp.org/2014/\">WordCamp SF 2014</a> was a few days later, I stayed and attended it also.</p>\n<p>Meeting and interacting with people from WordPress community was a very good experience, so this year I am traveling to US only to attend WordCamp US.</p>\n<p>As I am coming only to &#8220;attend&#8221;, I will have ample time to chat about many things.</p>\n<p>Below is the itinerary of my US trip:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>30th Nov &#8211; 2nd Dec <a href=\"http://www.hostelnewyorkny.com/\">New York City (Manhattan)</a></li>\n<li>3rd &#8211; 7th Dec  &#8211; Philadelphia &#8211; <a href=\"https://2015.us.wordcamp.org/\">WordCamp US</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can simply send me a tweet <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rahul286\">@rahul286</a> to catchup or leave a comment on this blog post.</p>\n<p>The best way to recognise me would be look out for a guy wearing a t-shirt with rtCamp logo. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/72x72/1f609.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-131010 size-large\" src=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/WordCamp-US-2015-720x379.png\" alt=\"WordCamp-US-2015\" width=\"640\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/WordCamp-US-2015-400x210.png 400w, https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/WordCamp-US-2015-720x379.png 720w, https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/WordCamp-US-2015.png 916w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Link:</strong> <a href=\"https://2015.us.wordcamp.org/\">WordCamp US 2015</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/lets-catch-up-wordcamp-us-2015/\">Let&#8217;s Catch Up at WordCamp US 2015</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"BuddyPress 2.4.0 “Pietro” Released with Contributions by rtCampers\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/buddypress-2-4-0-pietro-released-contributions-rtcampers/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 12 Nov 2015 15:10:47 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"BuddyPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"BuddyPress Core Contribution\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"rtCampers\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://rtcamp.com/?p=130029\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:373:\"<p>Latest version of BuddyPress 2.4.0 \"Pietro\" is released by core contributions by 3 rtCampers.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/buddypress-2-4-0-pietro-released-contributions-rtcampers/\">BuddyPress 2.4.0 “Pietro” Released with Contributions by rtCampers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Parth Pandya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2430:\"<p><a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/buddypress-2-4-0.png\" rel=\"lightbox[130029]\"><img class=\"size-large wp-image-130030 alignnone\" src=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/buddypress-2-4-0-720x283.png\" alt=\"buddypress-2-4-0\" width=\"640\" height=\"252\" srcset=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/buddypress-2-4-0-400x157.png 400w, https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/buddypress-2-4-0-720x283.png 720w, https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/buddypress-2-4-0.png 790w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a></p>\n<p>BuddyPress 2.4.0 &#8211; “Pietro” was released yesterday named after an Italian native owning 3 fancy Italian restaurants in the French capital.</p>\n<p>Version 2.4.0 brings over a hundred improvements that includes bug fixes and features enhancements. Users of the previous version will experience improved template hierarchy with customizations and auto-adjustments of the Drag &amp; Drop image to your device.</p>\n<p>Here’s your bite at the BuddyPress 2.4.0 “Pietro” on <a href=\"https://buddypress.org/2015/11/buddypress-2-4-0-pietro/\">its release post</a>.</p>\n<h2>rtCampers on BuddyPress</h2>\n<p>rtCamp has a few products that are popular with BuddyPress users and hence our developers take a lot of pride in being part of the WordPress community and contribute to BuddyPress.</p>\n<p>We are proud and inspired to see our very own <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mehulkaklotar/\">Mehul Kaklotkar</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pareshradadiya/\">Paresh Radadiya</a> and <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ritteshpatel/\">Ritesh Patel</a> have their names up as contributors to BuddyPress 2.4.0 “Pietro”.</p>\n<p>You can read up about previous <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/tag/buddypress-core-contribution/\">BuddyPress core contributions here</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Link: </strong><a href=\"https://buddypress.org/2015/11/buddypress-2-4-0-pietro/\">BuddyPress 2.4.0 – “Pietro” Release Post</a></p>\n<p><strong>Related:  </strong><a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/tag/wordpress-core-contribution/\">WordPress Core Contributions</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/buddypress-2-4-0-pietro-released-contributions-rtcampers/\">BuddyPress 2.4.0 “Pietro” Released with Contributions by rtCampers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"Introducing Shmart Addon for Easy Digital Downloads\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-payment-gateway-easy-digital-downloads-plugin/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 21 Oct 2015 14:49:43 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Easy Digital Downloads\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"premium\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Shmart\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://rtcamp.com/?p=119261\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:381:\"<p>A WordPress plugin that integrates Shmart payment service which is popular in India, with your Easy Digital Downloads store.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-payment-gateway-easy-digital-downloads-plugin/\">Introducing Shmart Addon for Easy Digital Downloads</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aditya Kane\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2684:\"<p><a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2015/10/shmart.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[119261]\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-121606 alignright\" src=\"https://rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2015/10/shmart.jpg\" alt=\"shmart\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" /></a>It has been a year, since <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/moving-woocommerce-easydigitaldownloads/\">we started using Easy Digital Downloads</a>. Since we are based out of India, we wanted to make it easy for our Indian users to make payments using Shmart payment gateway.</p>\n<p>Shmart is an Indian payment gateway. It allows users to make payments in INR currency. You can check out more details at <a href=\"http://shmart.in\">shmart.in</a>. In India Shmart is one of the few payment gateway which allows to sell software.</p>\n<h2>Shmart Addon for Easy Digitial Downloads plugin</h2>\n<p>Since there was no ready made solution, we developed an addon for Easy Digital Downloads that allows users to accept money in INR currency using Shmart service from India.</p>\n<p>We have been using this addon on our own store along with Easy Digital Download for a while now. After polishing the code a bit, we are now releasing it as an premium plugin.</p>\n<p>Here is a short video demo of the plugin.</p>\n<p><iframe class=\"wistia_embed\" src=\"//fast.wistia.net/embed/iframe/5qyo4thqlz\" name=\"wistia_embed\" width=\"770\" height=\"461\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe><br />\n<script src=\"//fast.wistia.net/assets/external/E-v1.js\" async=\"\"></script></p>\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Your website will require <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\">Easy Digital Download</a> plugin.</li>\n<li>Shmart approved account to get all the required keys.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://openexchangerates.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://openexchangerates.org/</a> free or paid API access to convert foreign currency into INR.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The price of this plugin is $49 USD for a single site licence.</p>\n<p>You can read the complete <a href=\"http://docs.rtcamp.com/easydigitaldownloads-shmart-payment-gateway/\">documentation here</a>.</p>\n<p><a class=\"primary button\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/products/easydigitaldownloads-shmart-payment-gateway/\">BUY PLUGIN</a></p>\n<p><strong>Related: </strong>Are you running an e-commerce store on WordPress? Try out <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/products/rtbiz-helpdesk/\">rtBiz Helpdesk</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-payment-gateway-easy-digital-downloads-plugin/\">Introducing Shmart Addon for Easy Digital Downloads</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:29:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";a:16:{s:6:\"server\";s:5:\"nginx\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Mon, 29 Feb 2016 18:25:16 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:1